          <h2>What is collaboration?</h2>
          
          <div class="dictionary-definition">
          <h3>Collaboration</h3>
          <p>The action of working with someone to produce something.</p>
          <cite>Oxford English Dictionary</cite>
          </div>
          
          <p>Effective collaboration is essential to the management of group projects. Collaboration allows different members of the group to contribute to the project that is being worked on, with each member bringing their own strengths and ideas.</p>
          <p class="question-marks">Working in a team can be tricky. How often should you communicate and in what form? Is email really the best way of letting others know what's going on? In recent years a range of new software solutions have been developed. All of these tools have one thing in common. They are all web-based so can be accessed from anywhere in the world, and they address lots of the key issues when working with others. Let's focus on four of these tools.</p>
          
          </div>
          
