              <p>Slack is a tool which enables teams to communicate with each other. Group discussions can be organised into channels, and all messages and shared documents are stored and searchable, so every decision is catalogued.</p>
              <h4 class="software-type-helps-title">The way it improves collaboration</h4>
              <div class="software-type-helps-box">
