              <p>Trello is a project management application. Tasks can be created, prioritised and assigned meaning that an overview of project progress can be seen by anyone at any time. Visuals can be uploaded and seen in Trello, allowing people to comment and approve.</p>
              <h4 class="software-type-helps-title">The way it improves collaboration</h4>
